dev.nokee.platform.nativebase

Interface OperatingSystemFamily

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    OperatingSystemFamily
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface OperatingSystemFamily
    Represents the operating system family of a configuration. Typical operating system family include Windows, Linux, and macOS.

    Note: This interface is not intended for implementation by build script or plugin authors.

    Since:
    0.1
